{{!
  PROFILE CUSTOM CONTENT SNIPPET

  Adds the Inklings tab content to the character profile page.

  FILE: ares-webportal/app/templates/components/profile-custom.hbs

  STEP 1: Locate the file
  1. Open your game's ares-webportal/app/templates/components/profile-custom.hbs

  STEP 2: Find the insertion point
  2. Find the <div class="tab-content"> element
  3. Look for the closing </div> tag for that tab-content div
  4. The new tab-pane should go INSIDE the tab-content, right before the </div>

  STEP 3: Copy and paste
  5. Copy the entire <div class="tab-pane"> block below (between the markers)
  6. Paste it inside the tab-content div at the end (before </div>)
  7. Save the file

  IMPORTANT DETAILS:

  ID MATCHING:
  - The id="inklings-tab-pane" below MUST match the href in profile-custom-tabs.snippet.hbs
  - Do NOT change this value

  PROPERTY NAMES:
  - This snippet uses: this.char.id, this.viewer.id, this.viewer.isStaff
  - These MUST match the property names your profile-custom.hbs actually uses
  - Common variations: character vs char, user vs viewer
  - If your template uses different names, update all three above

  ABOUT THE COMPONENT:
  The {{inklings-tab}} component displays all Inklings for a character:
  - View existing Inklings
  - Create new ones
  - Add messages and rolls
  - Submit for staff review
  - Share with other characters/groups
  - Changes save immediately (not part of profile save flow)
}}

{{! ---START COPY HERE--- }}
<div class="tab-pane fade" id="inklings-tab-pane">
  {{inklings-tab characterId=this.char.id viewerId=this.viewer.id isStaff=this.viewer.isStaff}}
</div>
{{! ---END COPY--- }}
